<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Self-help Toolkits - VibingSG</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7b2ff7, #f107a3);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border-top-left-radius: 20px;
      border-top-right-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .logo span {
      color: #66f0ff;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    main {
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #7b2ff7;
    }
    .resource {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .resource img {
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 15px auto;
      width: 70%;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    footer {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7b2ff7, #f107a3);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      font-size: 1em;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 20px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 20px;
    }
  .video-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .video-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .video-thumb {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
    .video-content {
      padding: 15px;
    }
    .video-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #7b2ff7;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .video-desc {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .watch-link {
      color: #7b2ff7;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo" style="font-size: 1.8em;">Vibing<span>SG</span></div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/toolkits">Resources</a>
      <a href="/support">Helpline</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
  <h2>Self-help Toolkits</h2>
  <p>Explore curated tools and articles to support your mental wellness and academic success.</p>
  <div class="video-grid">

    <div class="video-card">
      <img src="images/Breathe.png" alt="Deep Breathing" class="video-thumb">
      <div class="video-content">
        <div class="video-title">Deep Breathing</div>
        <div class="video-desc">Practice calm breathing exercises with this interactive tool from Calm.</div>
        <a href="https://www.calm.com/breathe" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Open Breathe →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-card">
      <img src="images/Timer.png" alt="Pomodoro Counter" class="video-thumb">
      <div class="video-content">
        <div class="video-title">Pomodoro Timer</div>
        <div class="video-desc">Use the Pomodoro timer to boost your focus and productivity.</div>
        <a href="https://pomodorotimer.online/" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Open Timer →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-card">
      <img src="images/Chatbot.png" alt="Chat with a Bot" class="video-thumb">
      <div class="video-content">
        <div class="video-title">Chat with a Bot</div>
        <div class="video-desc">Have a confidential chat with a wellbeing bot to explore your emotions.</div>
        <a href="https://mindline.sg/youth/assessment?wysa-tool-id=default" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Open Chat →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-card">
      <img src="images/StressMgmt.png" alt="Stress Management" class="video-thumb">
      <div class="video-content">
        <div class="video-title">Stress Management</div>
        <div class="video-desc">Read practical strategies for managing stress from trusted local resources.</div>
        <li><a href="https://www.mindline.sg/youth/article/coping-with-stress?type=mood" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Coping with Stress</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.ncss.gov.sg/research-and-insights/community-resources/mental-well-being/for-youths" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Mental Well-being for Youths</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.mindline.sg/youth/article/building-resilience-in-singapores-youth?type=interest" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Building Resilience</a></li>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-card">
      <img src="images/ExamTips.png" alt="Exam Preparation Tips" class="video-thumb">
      <div class="video-content">
        <div class="video-title">Exam Preparation Tips</div>
        <div class="video-desc">Top strategies to study smart, reduce anxiety, and ace your exams.</div>
        <li><a href="https://www.topuniversities.com/student-info/health-and-support/exam-preparation-ten-study-tips" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Top 10 Study Tips</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://blog.cambridgeinternational.org/tips-for-effective-exam-preparation/" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Effective Exam Preparation</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.psb-academy.edu.sg/blog/study-tips-how-to-be-exam-ready" target="_blank" class="watch-link">How to be Exam-Ready</a></li>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-card">
      <img src="images/Time Management.png" alt="Time Management" class="video-thumb">
      <div class="video-content">
        <div class="video-title">Time Management Tips</div>
        <div class="video-desc">Learn to organize your time better with proven productivity techniques.</div>
        <li><a href="https://todoist.com/productivity-methods/pomodoro-technique" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Pomodoro Technique</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.skillsyouneed.com/ps/time-management.html" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Essential Time Management</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.mindtools.com/pages/main/newMN_HTE.htm" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Time Management Tools</a></li>
        </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>
<footer>
    <p>A mental wellness web application designed for Singaporean teenagers to manage academic stress through mood tracking, journaling, self-help resources, and educational content.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
